Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:09.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:26.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:51.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:02.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:12.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:09.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何处寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前这冷酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:26.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理无从寻觅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}仅有肮脏的抢与夺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一场派对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命运纵横交错的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向着终点一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论胜者或败者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或许某物已然疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑问为何…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:51.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切尽皆消失在这片虚无之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}现在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:02.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高举这份决心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:05.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}来吧  继续BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:12.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束缚  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:15.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们只需变得疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需变得疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至疯狂  疯而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦或地狱  GO CRY GO
